<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Deleted - <%= appName %>
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #d9534f;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Account Deleted</h2>
        <p>Dear <strong>
                <%= fullName %>
            </strong>,</p>
        <p>We regret to inform you that your account has been permanently deleted from <strong>
                <%= appName %>
            </strong>.</p>
        <p>If you believe this was a mistake or have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your time with us.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= year %>
                <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>